latestIgtvVideos.title: #bettertogether
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Where there is a woman, there is magic💫
And that is what these absolutely stunning creators who we are giving a tribute to through our video have been creating since years! 
Each one of you inspire us every day with your passion for style, your consistency, your commitment towards your work, your creativity but most importantly the fact that you HUSTLE each day!
Thank you to all of you stunning women, whose style we have tried to recreate in this video for inspiring all of us each day! We promise to take the legacy forward! 
Lastly, thanks to each women out there for just being you, remember, each of you are unique in your own way!
Happy International womens day ladies!❤️❤️
